#- §lAct 5§0
§0
§0§l[Scene 1]§0
§0
§7§oEnter Shadedjon§0
§0
§1Shaded:§0 bum-ba-da-dum-ba, so nice to be in love§0
§0
§7§oEnter Nightwinga
#- §1Shaded:§0 Night! What news do you have from Mount Augusta? What of my beautiful Sintralin?§0
§0
§1Nightwinga:§0 uhhhh... yeah she's dead RIP.
#- §1Shaded:§0 what? Noooooooo, you know where I sleep, get me a pen and paper I must write a letter.
#- §1Nightwinga:§0 hmm I think it's a bad idea and you might do something stupid, but this character is short-lived enough for me to just leave with no suspicions aroused. Ok.§0
§0
§7§oNightwinga exits.
