§0
§1Xavter:§0 someone approaches.
#- §7§oEnter Shadedjon§0
§0
§1Shaded:§0 the news is true, such black, terrible news. Oh how my grief threatens to overwhelm me. Nay, it has overwhelmed and now spills under, pulling me down to the riptide of its own wake.
#- §1Xavter:§0 bruh why don't you back off my girl, ok?§0
§0
§1Shaded:§0 my grief is too great.§0
§0
§1Xavter:§0 aight man you need a minute, I get it. I'll leave you here.§0
§0
§1Shaded:§0 thanks
#- §1Xavter:§0 §7§o[aside]§0 is he laying on the bed? That some kinky shit.§0
§0
§1Shaded:§0 please, my love, one last...
#- §1Xavter:§0 alright enough of that you sick twisted motherfucker. I'm gonna pearl you for defiling the grave and violation of your banishment. And because you're a fucking weirdo.§0
§0
§1Shaded:§0 do you provoke me?
#- §1Xavter:§0 fite me.§0
§0
§1Shaded:§0 PNG!§0
§0
§7§oThey fight. Xavter §7§opops.§0
§0
§1Xavter:§0 please... leave my pearl with my beloved... where it belongs...
#- §1Shaded:§0 I will do this because your love is true.§0
§0
§1Xavter:§0 uhhg.... Gaaay.... Ughhg
#- §1Shaded:§0 now I must at last do my last act, of love and defiance. Goodnight, Sintralin, and this cruel world that hath separated us. Bumps Sintralin, then drinks harming potion and dies.
#- §7§oEnter Sashimii§0
§0
§1Sash:§0 FUCK. It appears I am too late. Fuck fuck fuck fuck fuck. Fuck. Shit. Fuuuuuck.
#- §7§oEnter Nightwinga§0
§0
