#- §7§oEnter ttk2§0
§0
§1Ttk2:§0 what is happening over here that is causing such a TPS dro- oh. Dreadful.§0
§0
§7§oEnter Papa and §7§oJFcamp§0
§0
§1Papa:§0 why has our grief been disturbed?
#- §1JFcamp:§0 in the streets of Mount Augusta they shout "Shaded dies!" and others say "Sintralin dies!" while still others say "Xavter dies!".§0
§0
§1Ttk2:§0 A scene of woe, it would appear.§0
§0
§7§oEnter Itaqi§0
§0

#- §1Ttk2:§0 Itaqi, come see your beloved friend and ally lie dead.§0
§0
§1Itaqi:§0 hm, same just happened to Max. He couldn't handle the idea of Shaded being banished, so he perished. Seeing Shaded dead oooh rip, I have lost so many so soon.
#- §1Ttk2:§0 seal this place up, I will world edit the grief away later. You two have both loved and lost. Now, in the grief of your fallen friends and Xavter, make peace between your groups. Eden and Nox should fight no more!
#- §1Itaqi:§0 too many have died.§0
§0
§1Papa:§0 indeed. Perhaps it's time to set aside petty grievances.§0
§0
§1Itaqi:§0 and end this cycle of reps.§0
§0
§1Papa:§0 no more war, Itaqi
#- §1Itaqi:§0 only peace now, Papa§0
§0
§1Ttk2:§0 let us erect a new vault, the Shadedjon and Sintralin Memorial vault, and have it hold all your pearls. Together, in your prison, will we end this war.
#- §1Itaqi:§0 agreed§0
§0
§1Papa:§0 agreed.§0
§0
§1Ttk2:§0 so was the gloomy story of peace brought my misery, memes and shitposts. So is the story of Shaded and Sintralin.
